Hilt
    - Component lifetimes https://developer.android.com/training/dependency-injection/hilt-android#component-lifetimes
        - Hilt automaticamente cria e destroi instancias de classes de componentes gerados, seguindo
        o ciclo de vida das classes Android correspondentes. Abaixo segue os componentes e
        quando eles sao criados e destruidos as instancias conforme o ciclo de vida

        - Component                 |  created at               | destroyed at
          SingletonComponent           Application#onCreate         Application destroyed
          ActivityRetainedComponent    Activity#onCreate()          Activity#onCreate()

          ViewModelComponent           ViewModel#onCreate           ViewModel destroyed
          ActivityComponent            Activity#onCreate()          Activity#onCreate()
          FragmentComponent            Fragment#onAttach            Fragment#onDestroy
          ViewComponent                View#super                   View destroyed
          ViewWithFragmentComponent    View#super                   View destroyed
          ServiceComponent             Service#onCreate             Service#onDestroy


